    Package Description
    com.ibm.watson.developer_cloud.question_and_answer.v1
    The Question and Answer service interprets and answers user questions directly based on primary data sources (brochures, web pages, manuals, records, etc.) that have been selected and gathered into a body of data or 'corpus'.
